Third-party software
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

octo-mail vendors its Go module dependencies under vendor/. Each vendored
module retains its own upstream license file (LICENSE / NOTICE) in its
directory under vendor/; those license terms govern the corresponding code and
are distributed with this repository.

Notably, octo-mail reuses the pure-protocol libraries of mox
(github.com/mjl-/mox) as an unmodified library dependency. mox is dual-licensed
under the MIT License and the Mozilla Public License 2.0; octo-mail uses it
under the terms of the MIT License. See:

  vendor/github.com/mjl-/mox/LICENSE.MIT
    Copyright 2021 Mechiel Lukkien <mechiel@ueber.net>

For a full inventory of vendored modules and their licenses, see the license
files under vendor/ (e.g. `find vendor -iname 'LICENSE*' -o -iname 'NOTICE*'`)
or run `go mod download -x` / inspect go.mod.
